## Successful Select Product with Index and Add to Cart
Tags: successful

If there is a product related to the search phrase, related results are listed
Select an element by specifying data index number
Add to cart

* Go to the Amazon homepage
* Accept cookies
* Search "Automate The Boring Stuff With Python"
* Click to the shipped by Amazon checkbox
* Select products element "1"
* Add to cart

